#+Title: new arch install

* install 

[[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PQgyW10xD8s&t=360s][arch install]]

[[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pouX5VvX0_Q][xorg and window manager]]

[[https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/Mac#Early_2015_13%22/15%22_-_Version_12,x/11,4+][arch wiki on mac install]]


* packages


#+begin_src shell
sudo pacman -S zsh xorg xorg-xinit alacritty git emacs picom qtile rofi ttf-fira-code firefox neovim nitrogen nodejs vim xf86-video-intel discord
#+end_src

* dotfiles

make the bare git repo 

#+begin_src shell
git init --bare $HOME/dotfiles
#+end_src

pull all the dotfiles

#+begin_src shell
/usr/bin/git --git-dir=$HOME/dotfiles/ --work-tree=$HOME pull origin master
#+end_src

